title: How Seahawks can save Russell Wilson, Dez in Green Bay? (Football 05/16)
description:
Pete Prisco joins Will Brinson to talk about the latest NFL news, including Dez Bryant as finding a potential landing spot in Green Bay or New Orleans, Adrian Peterson returning to New Orleans, how the Seahawks can save Russell Wilson and then the guys break down the offseasons for the Falcons and Buccaneers and discuss those respective teams win totals for 2018. Prisco is optimistic! Sound the siren!
